### ================================================================
### Product Service - 외부 API 테스트
### 실행 전: http-client.env.json의 hubId, companyId 값을 채워넣을 것
### ================================================================

### [1] 상품 생성 (MASTER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "hubId": "{{hubId}}",
  "name": "테스트 상품",
  "price": 10000,
  "stock": 100
}

> {%
  // 응답에서 productId를 환경변수에 자동 저장
  client.global.set("productId", response.body.data.id);
  client.test("상품 생성 성공", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 201, "status 201 expected");
    client.assert(response.body.data.id !== null, "productId 반환 필요");
  });
%}

### ================================================================

### [2] 상품 목록 조회 (MASTER - 전체)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
X-User-Role: MASTER

### [3] 상품 목록 조회 (이름 검색)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?name=테스트
X-User-Role: MASTER

### [4] 상품 단건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

### ================================================================

### [5] 상품 수정 (MASTER - 이름/가격 변경)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "name": "수정된 상품명",
  "price": 15000
}

### [6] 재고 수정 (MASTER)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "stock": 200
}

### ================================================================

### [7] 상품 삭제 (MASTER)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

### ================================================================
### 권한 검증 테스트
### ================================================================

### [8] 상품 생성 실패 - 존재하지 않는 companyId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "companyId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099",
  "hubId": "{{hubId}}",
  "name": "실패 테스트",
  "price": 5000,
  "stock": 10
}

### [9] 상품 생성 실패 - 존재하지 않는 hubId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "hubId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099",
  "name": "실패 테스트",
  "price": 5000,
  "stock": 10
}

### [10] 상품 생성 실패 - 음수 가격
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
X-User-Role: MASTER

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "hubId": "{{hubId}}",
  "name": "음수 가격 테스트",
  "price": -1,
  "stock": 10
}
